10.4.1.4 Paccayapaccanīyānuloma
Mahantaraduka
Cittasampayuttaduka
Paṭiccavāra
Paccayapaccanīyānuloma
153.
2690Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe tīṇi, anantare tīṇi, samanantare tīṇi…pe…  aññamaññe cha…pe…  purejāte ekaṃ, āsevane ekaṃ, kamme nava…pe…  magge ekaṃ…pe…  avigate nava.
